and another point i want to make...how many of you really go to guk for exp? hehe. that's not why i went, although the exp is quite a bonus. <BR>
that's the primary reason why it's cool with me if someone 10 or more levels higher than me is in the group or waiting to group. i'm there for equipment to improve my character. i'll go to solB or kunark for mad exp :-)<BR>
